[SN]TITLE[SN]
Pontardawe woman taken to hospital after stabbing

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A woman has been taken to hospital after being stabbed in Neath Port Talbot.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
South Wales Police said they are investigating the serious assault which happened in Pontardawe at around 17:45 BST on Tuesday.
Police said a local woman in her 30s has been arrested in connection with the incident.
